data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! SELLERS VERY MOTIVATED! Don't miss this beautifully updated house!! The home has four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, new flooring, paint, fixtures, etc. It also features a large walk-out back porch with a huge yard and brand new wooden fence. The home comes equipped with a central air system to help beat the heat in the summer as well as a wood burning fireplace in the lower level to keep you warm during the cold winter months! This property is sure to please the entire family during the holidays! Come seize your opportunity to check out this wonderful home!
